CALCULATE( SUM(Sheet_Entry_View[units]), _Dates[FY] = fy, USERELATIONSHIP(_Dates[Date], Sheet_Entry_View[sheet_date])))  // Total units 
VAR diff_amount = amount - amount_prev  // Finds the difference
RETURN
